REMOVETRIGGER PREUPDATESCREEN
ON PREUPDATESCREEN SAVE QUICKSAND 1
ON PREUPDATESCREEN EXEC DrawCursor
REMOVETRIGGER POSTUPDATESCREEN
ON POSTUPDATESCREEN LOAD QUICKSAND 1

REMOVETRIGGER DrawCursor
ON DrawCursor DRAW ELEMENT:White CIRCLE X Y (BRUSHSIZE / 2)

// Notes:
// Don't forget to add radiation
// silicon still reacts with halogens and dilute alkalis
// Aluminium, when combined with Carbon, makes iron
// Titanium + Chlorine = Fire
// Zinc burns with a blue-green flame
// Hafnium(Melted flakes) and Cadmium fumes are explosive

EXEC setview 0 1 1 1 1 1 128
EXEC listelements
EXEC listgroups
SET BRUSHSIZE 15